  "detailed_description": "<h1>The author's words</h1><p>I am independently developing a game. Due to limited energy, there may be some cases that have not been fully tested. If you encounter any bugs or translation errors, please feel free to provide feedback through various channels!<br>Of course, if you have better ideas or suggestions, they are always welcome.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Fishy Fishy Swim\" is a relaxing and enjoyable placement game,<br>where you can also leave them in the fish tank to bring vitality and energy to your desktop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/7846cd1873fd510236b5e8510a586a7c.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/7846cd1873fd510236b5e8510a586a7c.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/7846cd1873fd510236b5e8510a586a7c.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the game, you can explore and collect different kinds of fish!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/b73aa58d0ee78b33905350970527dc69.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/b73aa58d0ee78b33905350970527dc69.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/b73aa58d0ee78b33905350970527dc69.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unique fishing system, different fishing equipment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/0c8b57799af1ee6abb889e3989feb071.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/0c8b57799af1ee6abb889e3989feb071.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/0c8b57799af1ee6abb889e3989feb071.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this game, you can collect more than a thousand different types of fish in total!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/eaba43ae411f22e72f832bdaed8d6a6f.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/eaba43ae411f22e72f832bdaed8d6a6f.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/eaba43ae411f22e72f832bdaed8d6a6f.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can also put them into the aquarium for display and earn income from ticket sales.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/61d526335a2c966fd92a030614a2880b.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/61d526335a2c966fd92a030614a2880b.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/61d526335a2c966fd92a030614a2880b.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "\"Fishy Fishy Swim\" is a relaxing and enjoyable placement game,<br>where you can also leave them in the fish tank to bring vitality and energy to your desktop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/7846cd1873fd510236b5e8510a586a7c.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/7846cd1873fd510236b5e8510a586a7c.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/7846cd1873fd510236b5e8510a586a7c.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the game, you can explore and collect different kinds of fish!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/b73aa58d0ee78b33905350970527dc69.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/b73aa58d0ee78b33905350970527dc69.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/b73aa58d0ee78b33905350970527dc69.mp4?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unique fishing system, different fishing equipment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/0c8b57799af1ee6abb889e3989feb071.poster.avif?t=1739887340\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962220/extras/0c8b57799af1ee6abb889e3989feb071.webm?t=1739887340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs